headline: DoorDash Announces Pricing of Upsized $2.5 Billion Convertible Senior Notes Offering
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, May 28, 2025--DoorDash, Inc. (NASDAQ: DASH) ("DoorDash"), a leading local commerce platform globally, today announced the pricing of $2.5 billion aggregate principal amount of 0% convertible senior notes due 2030 (the "notes") in a private offering to persons reasonably believed to be qualified institutional buyers pursuant to Rule 144A under the U.S. Securities Act of 1933, as amended (the "Securities Act"). The size of the offering was increased from the previously announced $2.
